DBT Core Installation
-Prerequisites
##Python
##VS Code
##Snowflake Trial Account

-Steps
--I had python 3.14. DBT Core is compatible with 3.12 or below. So I downgraded version to 3.12.
--VS Code Terminal - Go to cd "C:\Users\Desktop\DBT Prep\DBT_Project"
--Create Virtual Environment - python -m venv dbt-env
--Activate venv - dbt-env\Scripts\activate
--Install DBT Core and Snowflake adapter - pip install dbt-snowflake
--dbt --version (1.11.11 got installed)
